{"tid":221944,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"京官王振民暗指香港獨立","createTime":"2017-04-29T06:23:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-29T13:29:43.000Z","uid":82640,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2b1c69a9c45c00abe11f53b5ce1f248db76f34ae","tid":221944,"uid":82640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T06:23:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170429/s00001/1493437856644\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170429%2Fs00001%2F1493437856644&d=31jm0GaxjznMjcF0xOQh0p7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=f30be61c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170429%2Fs00001%2F1493437856644&h=a2e67bf8\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170429/s00001/1493437856644</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>王振民：若「兩制」威脅「一國」　無法繼續兩制安排</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n中聯辦法律部長王振民在港出席紀念《基本法》頒布27周年研討會。他表示，香港不能只見「兩制」不見「一國」，明言如果有人拿「兩制」對抗、損害「一國」，甚至以此作藉口「鬧獨立」，威脅到國家存在，那麼任何國家都「無法繼續兩制安排」。他說，一旦一國兩制失敗，「國家損失的是面子，但香港損失的是裏子，因此只許成功、不許失敗」。<br />\n<br />\n「兩制」威脅「一國」，無法繼續兩制安排<br />\n建議香港獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n繼陳佐耳後又一支持香港獨立京官"},{"pid":"4ccc02e9aa9ec4c95045fabfe17cef8fc7451301","tid":221944,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T06:24:44.000Z","msg":"他說，一旦一國兩制失敗，「國家損失的是面子，但香港損失的是裏子，因此只許港獨成功、不許失敗」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0310bc22cbf0568db309b7b65aed97f301924412","tid":221944,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T06:26:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>他說，一旦一國兩制失敗，「國家損失的是面子，但香港損失的是裏子，因此只許港獨成功、不許失敗」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係好痴線<br />\n依家京官為咗上位落老闆面可以去到幾盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db633c417ce6e073e72029c9368a308e0cdc64fc","tid":221944,"uid":31237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T06:28:19.000Z","msg":"未試過咁想有野失敗"},{"pid":"3e33d04b0c44881412cdab099a5961191fc2e369","tid":221944,"uid":35499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T06:30:06.000Z","msg":"兩國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2317907f87397589b045af8735c3f4cb014b72af","tid":221944,"uid":8157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T06:31:51.000Z","msg":"試下兩國兩制囉"},{"pid":"f25e41a411eae95315a467d08955e67fc4b9b631","tid":221944,"uid":82640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T07:27:22.000Z","msg":"王振民兩國論"},{"pid":"752a9e605f6fdc5f740dacb79bc743d5f2f75e27","tid":221944,"uid":17813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T07:30:50.000Z","msg":"大家識做啦，人哋叫你落中國面啊"},{"pid":"87ffbc6a8faddeff508e04111cbaaf91e78b2833","tid":221944,"uid":44323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T07:34:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大家識做啦，人哋叫你落中國面啊</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://hkpic.crntt.com/upload/201410/21/103438440.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkpic.crntt.com%2Fupload%2F201410%2F21%2F103438440.jpg&h=45388fd6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2fa2d7fc12449e61700935a87ba5b27daa22d280","tid":221944,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T09:02:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>大家識做啦，人哋叫你落中國面啊</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://hkpic.crntt.com/upload/201410/21/103438440.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%